<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear All,</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Thank you for joining us as we seek to transform thousands of young lives this summer through the NCS programme.&nbsp; We are incredibly excited about what is to come and hope that you are too.&nbsp; By way of introduction my name is Benny Goodman and I am the Director of Operations which means I am responsible for our NCS programme delivery.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">With our first programmes kicking off on Monday I wanted to write a short note to ask you to do 3 very important things:</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Firstly to say that&nbsp;<b>safety is about culture</b>.&nbsp; Whether we are talking about safeguarding, or live assessments of activity-related risks, the best mitigation against these threats is for all of our teams to establish a culture that takes safety seriously.&nbsp; My number one priority this year is to keep young people safe on NCS.&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>Where you see something that is not right, or just feels that it may not be right, please take action&nbsp;</b>– either stop it from happening or raise the issue immediately with the appropriate person.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Secondly to say that&nbsp;<b>we need your help.&nbsp; We MUST only ever refer to the programme as NCS</b>.&nbsp; Please never refer to it by the name of the organisation you are working for.&nbsp; As a co-founder of this organisation I am very proud of what we have and continue to achieve, but the money we are entrusted with is to run a programme called NCS.&nbsp; In the past it has been called otherwise, and so habits do need breaking, but it has never been more critical for you to change those habits.&nbsp; We are seeking to have a greater impact in the future by delivering more NCS places under an imminent new contract.&nbsp;&nbsp; It is therefore vital that:</p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; margin-left: 72pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">i)<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Young people therefore only ever talk about their experience of “NCS” (not that they have had a good time with us as an organisation per se)</p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; margin-left: 72pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">ii)<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>When not using their names, they are only referred to as young people or participants (and not a derivation of our organisation’s name as previously).</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Only you as staff can establish this terminology whilst on the programme –&nbsp;<u>please</u>&nbsp;help us to do this from the very start.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Thirdly,&nbsp;<b>do have a great time</b>&nbsp;and in doing so recognise your impact on the quality of the experience our participants will receive.&nbsp; As those with whom they are interacting daily, you have more impact than anything that can be set up in advance.&nbsp; You have been recruited because we are confident you will be fantastic – and our standards get higher each year – so please do give it all you can and you can be sure you will see changed lives as a result.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">All the very best as you work with us this summer, and I look forward to meeting many of you in the coming weeks.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Benny Goodman</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Director of Operations</p>]]></td>
